ActNational Aboriginal Economic Development Board Order
PrecisAppointment of NELLIE COURNOYEA of Inuvik, Northwest Territories, to be a member of the National Aboriginal Economic Development Board, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years; and designation of NELLIE COURNOYEA as Vice-Chairperson of the National Aboriginal Economic Development Board.
